articles.description: Jordy Kuiper and Demetrius Troy each scored 13 points, and UNC Greensboro pulled away from East Tennessee State to win the Southern Conference championship 62-47 on Monday night and earn its first NCAA Tournament berth since 2001.
articles.headline: UNC Greensboro smothers ETSU to win SoCon title 62-47

images.caption: It was a close game until late in the second half for East Tennessee State vs UNC Greensboro, until UNCG pulled away and won 62-47 to punch a ticket into the NCAA tournament.
images.name: UNC Greensboro wins Southern tournament

articles.description: Killian Tillie scored 26 points on 10-of-11 shooting, including connecting on all five 3-pointers, to lead No. 7 Gonzaga past San Francisco 88-60 on Monday night in the West Coast Conference Tournament semifinal game.
articles.headline: Tillie leads No. 7 Gonzaga over San Francisco

images.caption: Dick Vitale and Bob Wischusen discuss Gonzaga's dominating performance over San Francisco, including the impressive play of Killian Tillie who scores 26 points to help the Zags reach their 21st consecutive WCC championship game.
images.name: Breaking down Gonzaga's dominant victory

articles.headline: McGowens' FTs help NC A&T beat Delaware St. in MEAC tourney
